        </td>
        <td style="width:328px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">You can customize the views of any of the system tools to your own taste in the </text><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">View Composer</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. Ideally, in case something goes wrong, don&apos;t modify the system view itself but save down your changes with a new name. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">To open your custom view by default, simply go to the options for the tool in question (</text><text styleclass="Menu Command" translate="true">Tools/Options</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> menu) and change the</text><text styleclass="Class Name" translate="true"> #defaultView</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> aspect to the name of your custom view.</text></para>
        </td>
